
--- Run ---
1. Run Server on pc
2.Run app

--- Install App in Android Device ---
1. Connect android device to the pc with a cable 
2. On the phone: Settings -> About this device --> press build number as many times as required to unlock developers mode
3. Pair android ddevice to the computer via bluetooth
4. On the phone: Settings -> Developer Options --> USB Debugging (ENABLE)
5. Build the app from the Android Studio


--- Instalation PC server (optional - only for app testing) ---
1. Build the server (BluetoothServer_Communication)
